# Dantotsu AnimeKai Scraper

This is a web scraper for extracting anime data from **animekai.com** and formatting it in JSON for integration with **Dantotsu**.

## Features
✅ Scrapes anime titles, thumbnails, and episode links  
✅ Extracts video URLs for playback  
✅ Saves data in `output/dantotsu_animekai.json`  

## Installation
1. **Clone the repository:**  
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/dantotsu-animekai-scraper.git
   cd dantotsu-animekai-scraper
   ```
2. **Install dependencies:**  
   ```sh
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

## Usage
Run the scraper using:
```sh
python scraper.py
```
This will generate a JSON file with the scraped anime data.

## Output Format
```json
[
    {
        "title": "Anime Name",
        "link": "https://animekai.com/anime-url",
        "thumbnail": "https://animekai.com/thumbnail.jpg",
        "videos": [
            "https://animekai.com/video1.mp4",
            "https://animekai.com/video2.mp4"
        ]
    }
]
```

